name: Madr
body:
### Welcome to madr
This R package handles the post-processing from the Bayesian Uncertainty Characterization Framework MAD#: The Method of Anchored Distributions. To learn more about MAD#, visit mad.codeplex.com

### Authors and Contributors
Heather Savoy (@hsavoy)
